The paper deals with natural language understanding and proposes a new method for deriving natural language inference datasets from question answering datasets. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves learning a sentence transformation model, which could also fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
